de.axelwernicke.mypod.ipod
Class ITunesDBContentItem

java.lang.Object
  de.axelwernicke.mypod.ipod.ITunesDBContentItem
public class ITunesDBContentItem
extends java.lang.Object

A SongContent object stores the informations from the 'mhod' tag. mhod:
0x0000 'mhod' - tag
0x0004 24 - tag size
0x0008 - item size
0x000C - typ that specifies the content
0 - ??
1 - titel ( song or playlist )
2 - path
3 - album
4 - artist
5 - genre
'MPEG audio file' 6 - filetype
7 - equalizer settings
8 - comment
100 - playlist entry
0x0010 0 - unknown
0x0014 0 - unknown
0x0018 1 - position in playlist ( first is 1 )
0x001C - content size
0x0020 0 - unknown
0x0024 0 - unknown
0x0028 - content as unicode string

Author:
axelwe

for more details
